OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMurky, with extensive low cloud
OL,6,Fthat may bring a little patchy light
OL,7,Frain or drizzle. The cloud tending to
OL,8,Flift slowly into the afternoon but
OL,9,Fskies remaining generally cloudy.
OL,10,FSlightly milder than on Saturday for
OL,11,Fmost, with light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud tending to lower
OL,14,Fovernight with mist, patchy fog and
OL,15,Fhill fog becoming more widespread
OL,16,Fagain. Winds remaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
