OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAnother rather murky start to
OL,6,Fthe day on Monday but perhaps a better
OL,7,Fchance of some brighter intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping into the afternoon. Mostly
OL,9,Fdry, although the odd showery outbreak
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FBreezier through Tuesday, with cloud
OL,14,Fbreaks developing ahead of overnight
OL,15,Frain. Wednesday, early rain clearing,
OL,16,Fthen brighter and blustery with
OL,17,Fisolated showers. Windy Thursday,
OL,18,Fperhaps with a spell of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
